<ptxt>
<emph>
P0622: Generator Field / F Terminal Circuit
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
FR duty stays 0% for specified time while ECM commands generator to generate electricity.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(Type A and C: 3 D/C detection logic but mil does not light up)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(Type B: 2 D/C detection logic but mil does not light up)
</ptxt>
</entry>
